This git contains some of my config file:


    vim and nvim config (commented to help new users)
nvim/: hand built config (uses Vundle for plugin management)
vimrc: old vimrc config (in case I need a quick vim config without downloading Vundle)

    alacritty config
alacritty/: alacritty config file
alacritty_opacity/: is a brainless program to rewrite my alacritty opacity

     i3 config
i3/ 
i3blocks/ 

    zsh config (uses .oh-my-zsh)
zshrc 
custom.zsh-theme zsh custom theme


    wrappers scrits
pamixer_change_volume/: pamixer wrapper to allow +/- NUM operations
sc.sh: scrot wrapper
set_up.sh sets up most of my symlinks


gitconfig/: git profile


    xterm config
Xresources: xterm configs in case I need to use xterm instead of alacritty 

    bash config
bashrc: bash config in case I need to use it instead of zsh
